ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"就算係拍到拖咪又係累撚死人 我地呢d毒撚連係屋企打飛機都只係浪費緊紙巾 死左解決到問題都好d 死左都解決唔到問題先衰 晒撚埋老母老豆錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7d39c97a35fe55048463764ab417f3132fb3df","tid":232930,"uid":88731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T19:20:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係，入到U之後真係覺得好孤獨，無得同人交心。</blockquote><br />\n買隻公仔陪自己傾計啦，<br />\n做下Mr. Bean，<br />\n人生少愁思。</blockquote><br />\n依句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52329de414b40b0fe2b9966f1ddf18caba13b4be","tid":232930,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T09:38:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出黎做野後 約人仲難</blockquote><br />\n如果我話易左<br />\n你會唔會明白<br />\n我讀書果時係幾邊緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60230101b67ffa0cafe48f2bc0ed21a97c62cc0","tid":232930,"uid":99259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"我相信每個人都有自己既價值既～<br />\n我上年大學都識左好多朋友，日日都同佢地玩，係好開心好充實，<br />\n反而今年無同佢地玩，又無識新既人，好似變左另一個人咁，<br />\n但我好懷念以前同佢地玩既時間，立定決心再融入個陣，<br />\n有個朋友同我講，其實未必再融入番圈子就係好，隨住時間流逝關係一定會改變，<br />\n只要搵到自己既興趣價值就好了～<br />\n我發現而家重拾番玩音樂既樂趣都幾好呀！"},{"pid":"5870106034bf1e4ff8855e86ab9e2b70ed16aaf0","tid":232930,"uid":67462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:15:15.000Z","msg":"慣左孤獨就得架啦，獨左兩個sem習慣晒，麻木晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1727fd85d1f9077e84e54d93361b02e1ba878bf","tid":232930,"uid":72093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"Same 而家有新朋友都唔會傾得好入"},{"pid":"c802466c87f5006842f2e0ab7bf6273527f6fd0d","tid":232930,"uid":53534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我相信每個人都有自己既價值既～<br />\n我上年大學都識左好多朋友，日日都同佢地玩，係好開心好充實，<br />\n反而今年無同佢地玩，又無識新既人，好似變左另一個人咁，<br />\n但我好懷念以前同佢地玩既時間，立定決心再融入個陣，<br />\n有個朋友同我講，其實未必再融入番圈子就係好，隨住時間流逝關係一定會改變，<br />\n只要搵到自己既興趣價值就好了～<br />\n我發現而家重拾番玩音樂既樂趣都幾好呀！</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dd73e3b3e32f339bf06fefc1b5f0891d55c757","tid":232930,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:59:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7811ada60b11fd0c0a850a5d8c9baef5793e34d8","tid":232930,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T08:00:25.000Z","msg":"Iktfb<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}